{"tid":2164954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！聯合國安理會否決延長伊朗武器禁運　美國只得一國支持","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T02:46:35.000Z","uid":91914,"like":21,"dislike":278,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"e3647d87450ea3ae0c99519ed420451f342e68f5","tid":2164954,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"聯合國安全理事會表決延長伊朗武器禁運議案。8月14日公布的結果顯示，議案遭到安理會否決，其中只有兩國投下贊成票，包括美國和多米尼加共和國。歐洲國家全數棄權。<br />\n安理會有15個成員國，要通過延長武器禁運需要至少9票支持才能通過。除了美國和多米尼加共和國2票同意外，包括<span class=\"red\">英國、法國、德國等美國盟友在內的11個成員國均棄權。中國和俄羅斯則投下反對票。法案未獲通過。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國常駐聯合國代表張軍發表聲明，投票結果「再次說明單邊主義不得人心，霸凌行徑不會得逞」。美國國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）則指摘聯合國安理會未能果斷採取行動，捍衛國際和平和安全，形容是不可原諒。<br />\n<br />\nHK01"},{"pid":"5ca8e6f4bef44002454034d697aca41778c0a50d","tid":2164954,"uid":109428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:24:32.000Z","msg":"準備打"},{"pid":"d1e481c3a269dbf160a7a41c03ec55de920afb0f","tid":2164954,"uid":91914,"like":48,"dislike":2,"score":46,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:24:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成班左膠"},{"pid":"059900da5540401d9b86803a1be800afcd833cac","tid":2164954,"uid":127575,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"聯合國係支那 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e532bff068a9e5601db3953dbd78d99b92cf64bb","tid":2164954,"uid":143241,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"睇標題就估到一定係俄支兩國用否決權."},{"pid":"1b3334502043af9d1e6b8b6098d0d54bcab3bb83","tid":2164954,"uid":264245,"like":51,"dislike":4,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"01都唔擺返總共有幾多個國家可以投<br /